public static final class CampaignKitNotifier.CKAnalyticsType
extends java.lang.Enum

A category for the specific analytic event being recorded. Any of these may be recorded using the recordAnalytics() method in CampaignKitManager. However, in some cases, the Analytics will be recorded automatically by the Campaign Kit library. found: automatically recorded by this library when calling didFindCampaign. viewed: only for use with the recordAnalytics() event. fulfilled: only for use with the recordAnalytics() event.

See Also:
CampaignKitManager.recordAnalytics(com.radiusnetworks.campaignkit.CampaignKitNotifier.CKAnalyticsType, com.radiusnetworks.campaignkit.Campaign, com.radiusnetworks.campaignkit.Place), CampaignKitNotifier.didFindCampaign(Campaign), CampaignNotificationBuilder, Serialized Form
